    When the tide is very low, the water languishing on the sand makes for some very interesting patterns.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;干潮時
   &lt;/div&gt;
     干潮時には、砂の上に水がたまって、とても面白い模様になるんです。
   &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html">When the tide is very low, the water languishing on the sand makes for some very interesting patterns. 干潮時 干潮時には、砂の上に水がたまって、とても面白い模様になるんです。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04519.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04519.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Necklace</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220119/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Necklace" /><published>2022-01-19T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-19T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/necklace</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220119/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Kelp washed up on the beach.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ネックレス
   &lt;/div&gt;
     海岸に打ち上げられた真昆布。
   &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html">Kelp washed up on the beach. ネックレス 海岸に打ち上げられた真昆布。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04465.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04465.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Riviera</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220118/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Riviera" /><published>2022-01-18T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-18T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/riviera</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220118/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Walking on the beach, watching the sun set.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;リビエラ&lt;/div&gt;
   ビーチを歩きながら、夕日を眺める。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">Walking on the beach, watching the sun set. リビエラ ビーチを歩きながら、夕日を眺める。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04438.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04438.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunset at Topaz</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220116/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset at Topaz" /><published>2022-01-16T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-16T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/topaz</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220116/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Sun sets into the ocean in South Redondo Beach. Ten minutes later the rest of the sky lit up, below.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;トパーズ通りの夕焼け&lt;/div&gt;
   南レドンドビーチの海に沈む夕日。10分後、空の残りが照らされた（下）。
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;subimagegroup&quot;&gt;

    &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04385-Pano.jpg&quot;/&gt;   
&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">Sun sets into the ocean in South Redondo Beach. Ten minutes later the rest of the sky lit up, below. トパーズ通りの夕焼け 南レドンドビーチの海に沈む夕日。10分後、空の残りが照らされた（下）。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04355-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04355-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Korean Bell</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220114/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Korean Bell" /><published>2022-01-14T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-14T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/korean-bell</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220114/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    A drone view of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Korean_Bell_of_Friendship&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Korean Friendship Bell&lt;/a&gt; with the Pacific Ocean sunset behind. 
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;韓国の鐘&lt;/div&gt;
    太平洋の夕日を背にした&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.discoverlosangeles.com/jp/5%E6%9C%8815%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%9F%93%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD%E3%81%AE%E9%90%98&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;韓国友好の鐘&lt;/a&gt;をドローンで撮影したものです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="San Pedro" /><category term="Aerial" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">A drone view of the Korean Friendship Bell with the Pacific Ocean sunset behind. 韓国の鐘 太平洋の夕日を背にした韓国友好の鐘をドローンで撮影したものです。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_DJI_0062.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_DJI_0062.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hermosa Dusk</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220111/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hermosa Dusk" /><published>2022-01-11T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-11T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa-dusk</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220111/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;/220110&quot;&gt;Red sky&lt;/a&gt; reflects in the windows, last night in Hermosa Beach.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;美しい夕暮れ&lt;/div&gt;
    窓に映る&lt;a href=&quot;/220110&quot;&gt;赤い空&lt;/a&gt;、昨晩のハーモサビーチ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Strand" /><summary type="html">Red sky reflects in the windows, last night in Hermosa Beach. 美しい夕暮れ 窓に映る赤い空、昨晩のハーモサビーチ。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04235.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04235.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Red Sky Panorama</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220110/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Red Sky Panorama" /><published>2022-01-10T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-10T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/red-pano</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220110/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Clouds did not disappoint this evening in Hermosa Beach. In this panorama you can also see Malibu on the right side.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;赤い空パノラマ&lt;/div&gt;
    今晩のHermosa Beach の美しい雲。このパノラマでは右側にMalibu が見えています。 
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html">Clouds did not disappoint this evening in Hermosa Beach. In this panorama you can also see Malibu on the right side. 赤い空パノラマ 今晩のHermosa Beach の美しい雲。このパノラマでは右側にMalibu が見えています。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04179-HDR-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04179-HDR-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Foggy Marina</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220106/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Foggy Marina" /><published>2022-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/marina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220106/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
   Went to Marina del Rey for the sunset, but there was heavy fog when we got there. The opposite bank completely disappeared.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;霧のマリーナ&lt;/div&gt;
   夕日を見にマリーナ・デル・レイに行ったのですが、霧が濃くて。対岸が全く見えなくなってしまった。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Marina del Rey" /><category term="Fog" /><category term="Black and White" /><category term="Water" /><category term="Harbors" /><summary type="html">Went to Marina del Rey for the sunset, but there was heavy fog when we got there. The opposite bank completely disappeared. 霧のマリーナ 夕日を見にマリーナ・デル・レイに行ったのですが、霧が濃くて。対岸が全く見えなくなってしまった。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0123.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0123.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pelican Cove</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220105/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pelican Cove" /><published>2022-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pelican-cove</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220105/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
   Sunset at Pelican Cove in Rancho Palos Verdes. The Point Vicente Lighthouse is in the distance, at right.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ペリカン・コーブ&lt;/div&gt;
   ランチョ・パロス・バーデスのペリカン・コーブでの夕日。右手遠くに見えるのはポイントビセンテ灯台。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">Sunset at Pelican Cove in Rancho Palos Verdes. The Point Vicente Lighthouse is in the distance, at right. ペリカン・コーブ ランチョ・パロス・バーデスのペリカン・コーブでの夕日。右手遠くに見えるのはポイントビセンテ灯台。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03994-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03994-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hermosa Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220104/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hermosa Beach" /><published>2022-01-04T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-04T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220104/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Very small surf in Hermosa Beach, looking north to Manhattan Beach.   Kind of a companion to the &lt;a href=&quot;/220103/&quot;/&gt;previous photo&lt;/a&gt;, but the light was more diffused today.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ハーモサ・ビーチ&lt;/div&gt;
   ハーモサビーチの小さな波、北のマンハッタンビーチ方面を眺める。&lt;a href=&quot;/220103/&quot;/&gt;前の写真&lt;/a&gt;と大体同じですが、今日は光が拡散していました。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Very small surf in Hermosa Beach, looking north to Manhattan Beach. Kind of a companion to the previous photo, but the light was more diffused today. ハーモサ・ビーチ ハーモサビーチの小さな波、北のマンハッタンビーチ方面を眺める。前の写真と大体同じですが、今日は光が拡散していました。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0070.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0070.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>